---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Projects | MoreBetterLabs"
  description="MoreBetterLabs projects: Ruzuku online course platform, The Business of Courses, and the Course Lab Podcast."
  canonical="/projects/"
>
  <section class="pt-20 pb-8 sm:pt-28">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-5">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4" style="color: hsl(170 5% 95%);">
        Our Work
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg" style="color: hsl(170 5% 55%);">
        Everything we build starts from the same question: how do we help people learn better?
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-20 sm:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-5 space-y-16">

      <!-- Ruzuku -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3" style="color: hsl(170 60% 50%);">Flagship Product</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: hsl(170 5% 90%);">
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4" style="text-decoration-color: hsl(170 60% 50%);" rel="noopener">
            Ruzuku
          </a>
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: hsl(170 5% 55%);">
          An online course platform designed around learning science, not just content delivery.
          Ruzuku's step-by-step course structure, built-in discussions, and completion-focused design
          grew directly from research on how adults actually learn.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm space-y-1.5 mb-5" style="color: hsl(170 5% 45%);">
          <li>75,000+ courses hosted since 2011</li>
          <li>500,000+ students served worldwide</li>
          <li>Zero transaction fees</li>
          <li>Built-in email, discussions, and live workshops</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com" class="font-medium" style="color: hsl(170 60% 60%);" rel="noopener">
            Visit Ruzuku &rarr;
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com/features" style="color: hsl(170 5% 45%);" rel="noopener">
            Features
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com/pricing" style="color: hsl(170 5% 45%);" rel="noopener">
            Pricing
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style={`height: 1px; background: hsl(185 8% 12%);`}></div>

      <!-- Book -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3" style="color: hsl(170 60% 50%);">Book</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: hsl(170 5% 90%);">
          <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Business-Courses-Abe-Crystal/dp/1737374218" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4" style="text-decoration-color: hsl(170 60% 50%);" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            The Business of Courses
          </a>
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: hsl(170 5% 55%);">
          Everything I've learned from 13+ years helping course creators build sustainable online
          teaching businesses. Covers course design, pricing, launch strategy, student transformation,
          and building for the long term.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: hsl(170 5% 40%);">
          Published 2021 ·
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com/learn/book" style="color: hsl(170 60% 55%);" rel="noopener">Free chapter summaries</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style={`height: 1px; background: hsl(185 8% 12%);`}></div>

      <!-- Podcast -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3" style="color: hsl(170 60% 50%);">Podcast</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: hsl(170 5% 90%);">
          <a href="https://courselab.co/" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4" style="text-decoration-color: hsl(170 60% 50%);" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Course Lab Podcast
          </a>
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: hsl(170 5% 55%);">
          Weekly conversations with co-host Ari Iny about course creation, learning design,
          and building sustainable online teaching businesses. Produced in partnership with
          <a href="https://mirasee.com" style="color: hsl(170 60% 60%); text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: hsl(170 60% 50% / 0.4); text-underline-offset: 3px;" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mirasee</a>.
        </p>
        <a href="https://courselab.co/" class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: hsl(170 60% 60%);" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Listen to episodes &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>

      <div style={`height: 1px; background: hsl(185 8% 12%);`}></div>

      <!-- Learning Design Hub -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3" style="color: hsl(170 60% 50%);">Research & Writing</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: hsl(170 5% 90%);">
          <a href="/learning-design/" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4" style="text-decoration-color: hsl(170 60% 50%);">
            Learning Design Articles
          </a>
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: hsl(170 5% 55%);">
          Research-backed articles on learning design for practitioners. Translating learning science
          into practical frameworks for course creators — grounded in academic research at UNC, NC State,
          and UCLA, and tested through thousands of courses on Ruzuku.
        </p>
        <a href="/learning-design/" class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: hsl(170 60% 60%);">
          Read articles &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
